\pard\f0\fs28 {\b F. elastica} Roxb. ex Hornem.,{\i  Hort. Hafn. Suppl. }7 (1819), with entire, glossy, evergreen leaves, is commonly grown as a houseplant and, in the Mediterranean region, as a street tree.
\par

